asset.author: iRobot
asset.hookText: A marketing agency in the Chicago suburbs threw a bowling party for its creative teams in October of 2007. 10 days before the party they put together an online game asking people to keep track of robot bowling. To win the game, people had to try and match the robot's score on bowling night. This is frame #1.
